			<ul class="MainFeatures-body">
				<li>
					<h2>Lamp &amp; Mercury Free</h2>
					<h3>setting new standards</h3>
					
					<p>CASIO is setting an entirely new environmental standard thanks to it's new hybrid light source* 
					The Green Slim is an earth-friendly, low maintenance projector which eliminates the need for a short life (2000 hours typical) 
					mercury lamp & disposal. The Green Slim's lamp-free design has a 10X longer estimated life than a 
					CASIO mercury lamp projector, up to 20,000 hours without having to change a lamp.
					</p>
					<p>
					CASIO's new hybrid light source makes the frequent replacement and disposal of 
					conventional mercury lamps a thing of the past.
					</p>
					<p>
					<small>
					*The Green Slim Hybrid Light Source can only be replaced by the Casio Factory Service Center. 
					Disassembly of the projector and/or use of its technology or components for other purposes is 
					potentially dangerous and strictly prohibited.
					</small>
					</p>
					
					
				</li>
